org.drip.param.market

Class BasketMarketParamSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.service.stream.Serializer
      • org.drip.param.definition.BasketMarketParams
        • org.drip.param.market.BasketMarketParamSet

  • public class BasketMarketParamSet
extends BasketMarketParams
    This class provides an implementation of BasketMarketParamsRef for a specific scenario. Contains maps holding named discount curves, named credit curves, named treasury quote, named component quote, and fixings object.
